OL,3,CWhat does the two-child benefit cap
OL,4,Cbeing scrapped mean for the Midlands?
OL,6,FThe two-child benefit cap is being
OL,7,Fremoved at an estimated cost of #3
OL,8,Fbillion by 2029-30, according to the
OL,9,FOffice for Budget Responsibility.
OL,11,FA leaked OBR report says that they
OL,12,Fexpect 560,000 families to see an
OL,13,Fincrease in universal credit of #5,310
OL,14,Fby 2029. They estimate the cost of
OL,15,Fremoval will be #2.6 billion.
OL,17,FThe OBR suggest that 450,000 people
OL,18,Fwill be lifted out of poverty, and
OL,19,Fsome campaigners say it will pump
OL,20,Fhundreds of millions of pounds into
OL,21,Fthe poorest communities in Britain.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/14
